ActCanadian Commercial Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of DWAYNE LUCAS of Abbotsford, British Columbia, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Commercial Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Ken Sunquist, effective August 6, 2013.
